"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641314885,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"BiPXdvbfzk4lGFHllevxN8bYZHL4HsvEK9baFKiVaBg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x602576C10B46F6eFCc5d3Cfa178D281Fa817eB1F\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"3BuHK8q0p_rko89ZQM5EZyUnS55x4qa9KBM9vTKw7KI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"NFIS-390P0b_Hy7mLdpxUhMnBKS4-IPgdgdjm8WxbLk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"SHCO0GU_MH-OoR1BNbGhk9L7O34rl4IC261A1zqi_u68q10gUNhyGqsK88Kb15o8FY9Yi-Zui7MyiyY0ORjdZA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x691595f469274d593a4617d99610173f249c6cc17b3cda27aa5d02604afb597471113c2b5442a4cbdab80bc4004a2efecac7c26db9dc6930594bc3a9abc76a871b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"3BuHK8q0p_rko89ZQM5EZyUnS55x4qa9KBM9vTKw7KI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"NFIS-390P0b_Hy7mLdpxUhMnBKS4-IPgdgdjm8WxbLk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi